These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, fanta, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, baking, traveling, singing
1. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's hobby is baking##2
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking iced-tea##7
4. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | fanta | milk       | sprite | iced-tea        |
| Hobby      | traveling  | baking | singing        | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, pony, ferret
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, climbing, cricket, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the person who's sport is cricket and the owner of the pony##7
2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
3. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##5
4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is climbing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | pony | frog       | ferret         | bird     |
| Sport   | climbing   | surfing | cricket | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, epic, thriller
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, country, techno, folk
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the fan of folk##1
2. the fan of folk is somewhere between the fan of country and the fan of ambient##7
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the fan of ambient is somewhere between the fan of folk and the person watching satire movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | thriller | epic | adventure  |
| Music-Genre   | techno | ambient  | folk   | country |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, baking, singing, board-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, handball, rugby, basketball
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
3. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | baking | hiking | board-games       | singing |
| Sport   | handball      | parkour   | rugby | basketball  |

