.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, gardening, collecting, board-games
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, pakistani, mexican, polish
1. the polish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
2. the australian is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the polish is somewhere between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is woodworking##7
5. the polish is on the left of the mexican##1
6. the pakistani is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | collecting | woodworking   | board-games | gardening |
| Nationality   | australian      | pakistani | polish      | mexican |

