.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, milk, juice
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, french, pakistani, malaysian
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the pakistani##1
2. the pakistani is the person drinking juice##1
3. the french is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
6. the malaysian is somewhere between the canadian and the french##7
7. the pakistani is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | coffee      | milk | juice     |
| Nationality   | canadian    | malaysian | french   | pakistani |

