.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, apple, lemon, strawberry
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, german, australian, egyptian
1. the brazilian is on the far left##1
2. the person eating apple is on the left of the german##1
3. the person eating strawberry is on the far left or far right##3
4. the egyptian is somewhere between the person eating pear and the person eating lemon##7
5. the australian is somewhere to the left of the person eating lemon##5
6. the egyptian is on the left or right of the australian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | strawberry    | pear   | apple | lemon  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | australian | egyptian    | german |

