.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, nigerian, french, mexican
4 different pets are kept: turtle, ferret, mouse, rat
1. the nigerian is not the owner of the rat##6
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
3. the mexican is the owner of the mouse##1
4. the french is somewhere between the mexican and the canadian##7
5. the nigerian is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | mexican | french | nigerian | canadian |
| Pet           | mouse   | rat    | turtle       | ferret  |

