.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, martial-arts, drama, disaster
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, pony, turtle, fish
1. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere between the person watching zombie movies and the owner of the fish##7
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the owner of the turtle##6
3. the owner of the pony is not the person watching drama movies##6
4. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
5. the person watching zombie movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | disaster | martial-arts | drama |
| Pet           | hedgehog    | pony   | fish  | turtle      |

