4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person watching action movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the fan of disco##2
6. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere between the fan of disco and the person watching comedy movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
