4. the person who's hobby is chess is not the person driving the helicopter##6
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person driving the snowmobile and the person who's hobby is chess##7
7. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5

.:: Answer ::.
