The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, folk, disco, soul
1. the fan of folk is in an even position##4
2. the fan of soul is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the fan of disco##7
3. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
4. the fan of disco is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the fan of folk##5
6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the fan of disco##1
7. the person drinking milk is the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | juice   | coffee | milk | sprite   |
| Music-Genre   | techno | disco   | soul | folk |

