2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
5. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | hamster    | fish | rat     | rabbit |
| Transport   | helicopter | trike  | subway | ship |

 